{"tid":204343,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈 所有蚊已經進化左夜行生物","createTime":"2017-04-17T03:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T06:52:09.000Z","uid":90310,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44dba5d34189c9b38ece9f7d9665a349ad6170ae","tid":204343,"uid":90310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"基本上會on99係朝早咬人既蚊都比人類殺到七七八八<br />\n剩低既都係夜行既蚊<br />\n會等你訓左先咬你 又唔會咁易被你殺到<br />\n其實我講咁多只係想講<br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老母<br />\n連續幾晚係3點幾4點被人咬醒<br />\n但係我連佢個蚊影都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27edd6cfb5f026baf375b9c45efbe1854f765db","tid":204343,"uid":20914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上會on99係朝早咬人既蚊都比人類殺到七七八八<br />\n剩低既都係夜行既蚊<br />\n會等你訓左先咬你 又唔會咁易被你殺到<br />\n其實我講咁多只係想講<br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老母<br />\n連續幾晚係3點幾4點被人咬醒<br />\n但係我連佢個蚊影都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經發展到要噴蚊怕水瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2addb63a8bea5a3e061fdfb1852a819dd1d39e9","tid":204343,"uid":90310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:29:22.000Z","msg":"蚊呢種on9生物幾時先會絕種<br />\n仲黑人憎過曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709a84f2e6c74946a6a7f0606f1f70ea11bbc1e9","tid":204343,"uid":90310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>基本上會on99係朝早咬人既蚊都比人類殺到七七八八<br />\n剩低既都係夜行既蚊<br />\n會等你訓左先咬你 又唔會咁易被你殺到<br />\n其實我講咁多只係想講<br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老母<br />\n連續幾晚係3點幾4點被人咬醒<br />\n但係我連佢個蚊影都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經發展到要噴蚊怕水瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蚊怕水陣味都好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d445474aa0712ecf86199ee24629909cb1c816c","tid":204343,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:40:53.000Z","msg":"屋企用呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.gohappy.com.tw/images/product/101/3031561/430586_500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.gohappy.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fproduct%2F101%2F3031561%2F430586_500.jpg&h=4a165739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有時間制可SET 8,12,24小時, 我SET一日12小時, 長插唔洗理, 半個月都用唔到一支蚊香液, 蚊係少左好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad57e6232166f53875a70790ece57734da92efcc","tid":204343,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/chiajun69/1399389605-1708147691_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fchiajun69%2F1399389605-1708147691_m.jpg&h=5eb9e57d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b98a0c9a657daa0ac37716eb70c2cd91b294053","tid":204343,"uid":90310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企用呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.gohappy.com.tw/images/product/101/3031561/430586_500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.gohappy.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fproduct%2F101%2F3031561%2F430586_500.jpg&h=4a165739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有時間制可SET 8,12,24小時, 我SET一日12小時, 長插唔洗理, 半個月都用唔到一支蚊香液, 蚊係少左好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n硬係覺得依Ｄ化學物質會對身體唔好，所以無用到<br />\n我屋企係用電蚊拍殺蚊"},{"pid":"61dbc963ed7bb53447c116cc5b9d673eded7ba73","tid":204343,"uid":41138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UG08c95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUG08c95.jpg&h=c5078e65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12a8b025de2bf51f440c0a1ab4fbafa404771f6a","tid":204343,"uid":103826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"最衰就係耳邊嘈, 即刻醒哂<img sr